<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en-US"
      lang="en-US"
      metal:use-macro="here/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="passwordresettool">
<body>

<div metal:fill-slot="main"
     tal:define="global props python:container.portal_properties">
    
    <h1 class="documentFirstHeading" i18n:translate="heading_lost_password">Lost Password</h1>

    <p>
      Veuillez entrer votre identifiant dans l'espace prévu ci-dessous et validez. <a href="mail_login_form" class="tile" tabindex="-1"
                   tal:attributes="href string:${portal_url}/mail_login_form">
                  Identifiant oublié?
                </a>
      <br/> Si votre adresse email a changé, veuillez nous contacter par téléphone (081/724851) ou via <a href="contact-info"> le formulaire de la page contact.</a>
    </p>

    <form name="mail_password" 
          action="mail_password"
          method="post">
	
        <div class="row">
            <div class="label" i18n:translate="label_my_user_name_is">
            My user name is
            </div>
            <div class="field">
                <input name="userid"
                       type="text"
                       tabindex="" 
                       value=""
                       tal:attributes="value request/userid|nothing;
                                       tabindex tabindex/next | nothing;" 
                       />
                 <input class="context"
                       tabindex="" 
                       type="submit" 
                       value="OK"
                       tal:attributes="tabindex tabindex/next | nothing;"
                       />
            </div>
        </div>
    
    </form>

</div>

</body>
</html>
